INSERT INTO `wp_postmeta` VALUES (560, 394, '_aviaLayoutBuilderCleanData', '[av_slideshow size=\'no scaling\' animation=\'slide\' autoplay=\'true\' interval=\'5\']\r\n[av_slide id=\'536\' title=\'\' link=\'\' link_target=\'\'][/av_slide]\r\n[av_slide id=\'535\' title=\'\' link=\'\' link_target=\'\'][/av_slide]\r\n[/av_slideshow]\r\n\r\n[av_textblock]\r\n<h1 class="portpagefeatureh1">High-Performance Art At SEMA.</h1>\r\n<p class="portpagedatetext avia-align-center">Hyundai and ARK Performance create the Legato Genesis Coupe.</p>\r\n\r\n<img class="portpagedividerarrow avia_image avia-align-center" alt="divider arrow" src="/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/sectionDividerArrowGraphicDkGray.png" />\r\n[/av_textblock]\r\n\r\n[av_textblock ]\r\nThe Italian word “Legato” is a musical term which means a very smooth connection between the notes. For the 2013 SEMA Show, we partnered with ARK Performance to develop the Legato Concept Genesis Coupe, which seamlessly ties together exotic GT design, tuned performance and a premium interior experience.\r\n\r\nDesign-wise the Legato Concept retains the integrity of the production <a title="See More about the Genesis Coupe" href="https://www.hyundaiusa.com/genesis-coupe/">Genesis Coupe</a> trims, yet elevates them to concept car levels. The complete ARK Legato body treatment includes front and rear bumpers, side skirts, deck lid and wide-body cues, for a truly unique and integrated exotic performance look. A racing silver finish maximizes the nuanced design.\r\n\r\nUnder-the-hood modifications include a stock 3.8-liter Lambda V6 engine that’s been stroked to 4.0 liters for 400 horsepower and 425 lb.-ft. of torque. Inside the block, a Brian Crower (BC) 4.0 Stroker Kit with JE Pistons and BC 4340 crankshaft, connecting rods, and ARK oil cooler ensure maximum output with superior durability. An ARK intake system and headers enhance engine breathing at high rpm. For power delivery, an ARK dual-mass flywheel and carbon clutch kit ensure efficient power transfer to the pavement. An ARK DT-P coil-over suspension system coupled with Rays Engineering G25 wheels and Nitto NT05 tires ensure outstanding dynamic grip, while ARK carbon brake pads add fade resistance and stopping power.\r\n\r\nThe Legato interior is a top-of-the-line performance concept that includes Takata Drift Pro LE seats, AiM Sports Strada GT steering wheel, and a Rockford Fosgate® premium sound system.\r\n\r\nYou can see the ARK Legato Concept Genesis Coupe and our other high-powered concepts at the 2013 SEMA Show in Las Vegas, which runs from November 5 to 8.\r\n[/av_textblock]\r\n\r\n[av_textblock]\r\n<div id="morelinkbackdiv"><a class="seemorelinkback" href="https://www.hyundaiusa.com/genesis-coupe/">See More about the Genesis Coupe</a></div>\r\n[/av_textblock]\r\n\r\n[av_textblock]\r\n<div id="sharemenuholder"></div>\r\n[/av_textblock]\r\n\r\n[av_textblock]\r\n<p class="portpagerelstoriestext avia-align-center"><span style="color: #888888;">RELATED STORIES</span></p>\r\n\r\n<img class="portpagedividerarrow avia_image avia-align-center" alt="divider arrow" src="/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/sectionDividerArrowGraphicDkGray.png" />\r\n[/av_textblock]\r\n\r\n[av_portfolio categories=\'56\' columns=\'4\' items=\'4\' contents=\'excerpt\' preview_mode=\'auto\' image_size=\'portfolio\' linking=\'\' sort=\'no\' paginate=\'no\']\r\n\r\n') ; 
